# 🩺 Medical Chatbot using RAG, FAISS & Gemini

A Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) based Medical Chatbot that answers medical questions using information extracted from medical PDF documents. The application uses Google Gemini for response generation, FAISS for vector search, and Sentence Transformers for embeddings.

---

## 🚀 Features

* 📄 Load and process multiple PDF documents
* ✂️ Automatic text chunking for efficient retrieval
* 🔍 Semantic search using FAISS vector database
* 🤖 Google Gemini powered responses
* 🧠 Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)
* 🌐 Flask-based web application
* 💬 Interactive chatbot interface
* ⚡ Fast local inference and retrieval

---

## 🏗️ Project Architecture

PDF Documents
↓
Document Loader
↓
Text Chunking
↓
Sentence Transformer Embeddings
↓
FAISS Vector Store
↓
Retriever
↓
Google Gemini LLM
↓
Flask Web Application

